snippet.title: Irritated Mind: Fear of Warehouse Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Irritated Mind: Fear of the Warehouse is a first-person survival horror game with intense gameplay and a convoluted, horrifying storyline.

After a terrible tragedy, you must leave everything behind and start fresh in an unfamiliar city. A new job at a mysterious warehouse marks the beginning of your dark journey. Fate has prepared a place for you where secrets and dangers lurk around every corner.

Wishlist on Steam
Demo is coming soon!
